{"tid":1842842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"留意，醫管局已升至緊急級別 所有醫院謝絕探病","createTime":"2020-01-26T02:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T03:18:00.000Z","uid":295797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"651620c3de5bdf8cf5b1509018bb4fbd1335e61e","tid":1842842,"uid":295797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"醫管局琴晚已漏夜升級應變級別<br />\n<br />\n【醫院管理局啟動「緊急應變級別」】<br />\n <br />\n醫管局於一月二十五日宣布，因應政府就新型冠狀病毒最新情況，將本港應變級別由「嚴重」提升至「緊急」，公立醫院已相應啟動「緊急應變級別」，並會實施一系列特別措施，加強感染控制措施: <br />\n<br />\n- 所有公立醫院由即日起謝絕探病<br />\n- 所有進入及離開醫院、門診人士請清潔雙手<br />\n- 醫院、門診範圍內必須佩戴外科口罩<br />\n- 請遵守醫院、門診指示，量度體溫<br />\n- 必要情況下，訪客可能被要求登記身分，以便日後跟進<br />\n<br />\n更多資料: <a href=\"https://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/pad/200125Chi6.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ha.org.hk%2Fhaho%2Fho%2Fpad%2F200125Chi6.pdf&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=72a8d977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ha.org.hk/haho/ho/pad/200125Chi6.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n#醫院管理局<br />\n#緊急應變級別<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"4851ce16389bfbccc854a449c68b492cc3b75051","tid":1842842,"uid":295797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但最重要既喺大陸人依舊不斷排A&amp;E, 根本斬腳趾避沙蟲</span></span>"},{"pid":"9acd77a9dbb7667a0739c5a94f8e549607d92a89","tid":1842842,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">年初四就燒到嚟啦<br />\n快啲入去幫手推10下</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[集思廣益] 如果自己要封陸路口岸邊個地理上最容易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842861</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd3c63f2149b057e6ba2d1170daa8574d50bc447","tid":1842842,"uid":223114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTZUYVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTZUYVC.png&h=99d73e5f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}